body:
@karalabe . Please find the Grafana [snapshot](https://snapshot.raintank.io/dashboard/snapshot/Rpt4Tn4yiUW04ti2LYRFvjKgDYNby1Yu) . I was able to get the block processing time to less than 5 seconds but  guess it is still slow compared to the hardware provisioned 
`--cache=65536 --syncmode=full --gcmode=archive --datadir=/data/eth --nousb --maxpeers=20 --snapshot=false`.
Additionally, I could also see that the memory usage maxed at 30GB even though the cache set was 60 GB and the memory allocated to the pod is 90 GB.

@karalabe Please, provide the details, we are okay to send our Metrics to you.
My contact details:
arsenii.petrovich@altoros.com - email
@MrCommander - telegram

Please, let me know if this does not work for you and you prefer to chat via some other mean of communication ✌️
